data.description: Home, sweet home! Discover comfortable living at its finest in this inviting residence awaiting its new owners! You'll find a spacious living room for entertainment, a modern palette, abundant natural light, and a stylish wood-look & tile flooring combination. The eat-in kitchen boasts elegant granite counters, chic paneled cabinets, recessed lighting, and SS appliances. The well-proportioned main bedroom includes a walk-in closet and a private bathroom with dual sinks for added convenience. Venture outside to a covered patio in the backyard, offering plenty of room to craft your personal oasis. This value won't disappoint!
